                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I read fortunes in fairy breath. Yours says a hard road and a stubborn heart. Shall we test the second half?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Second warden. The mist answers to me here. Ready when you are."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Luna thinks the still pool grants wishes. Sweet of her. It collects reflections - it has kept a few of mine, and I mean to win them back."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "(She shuffles a deck in which every card is the same card.) The cards say you will win some. They decline to say which some."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Stella - second of the wardens",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
